---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
---

<PageLayout meta={{ title: "Oscar Gilg" }}>
	<section class="space-y-6">
		<h1 class="title">Oscar Gilg</h1>
		<p class="leading-relaxed">
			I work on AI welfare and persona representations at MATS 9.0, mentored by Patrick Butlin
			(Eleos AI). Previously equity options at Optiver, philosophy of consciousness with François
			Kammerer in Bochum, and Maths and CS at Oxford.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section class="mt-12">
		<h2 class="title text-accent mb-4 text-xl">Research and writing</h2>
		<ul class="space-y-3" role="list">
			<li>
				<span class="font-semibold">Shared preference representations across personas.</span>
				Forthcoming preprint, MATS 9.0 with Patrick Butlin. NeurIPS submission.
			</li>
			<li>
				<a
					class="cactus-link"
					href="https://www.lesswrong.com/"
					rel="noreferrer"
					target="_blank">Models have linear representations of what tasks they like</a
				>. Preliminary write-up from the same project (post link to be updated; code on GitHub).
			</li>
			<li>
				<span class="font-semibold">Split Persona Training.</span>
				SPAR 2025. Trigger-conditioned persona fine-tuning. Under review at ICML 2026 (avg review 4.5/6).
			</li>
			<li>
				<a class="cactus-link" href="https://github.com/oscar-gilg/zombuul" rel="noreferrer"
					>Zombuul</a
				>. Claude Code plugin for launching autonomous research agents on GPU pods.
			</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section class="mt-12">
		<h2 class="title text-accent mb-4 text-xl">CV</h2>
		<p>
			<a class="cactus-link" href="/cv.pdf">Download CV (PDF)</a>
		</p>
	</section>

	<section class="mt-12">
		<h2 class="title text-accent mb-4 text-xl">Contact</h2>
		<ul class="space-y-1" role="list">
			<li>Email: <a class="cactus-link" href="mailto:oscar.gilg18@gmail.com">oscar.gilg18@gmail.com</a></li>
			<li>
				GitHub: <a
					class="cactus-link"
					href="https://github.com/oscar-gilg"
					rel="noreferrer"
					target="_blank">github.com/oscar-gilg</a
				>
			</li>
			<li>
				LinkedIn: <a
					class="cactus-link"
					href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/oscar-gilg"
					rel="noreferrer"
					target="_blank">linkedin.com/in/oscar-gilg</a
				>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</section>
</PageLayout>
